OVERVIEW
====================================================================================================================

ReadByte is a simple Fortran routine to read individual bytes and 4/8-byte reals and integers from any
file. Developed and tested using gfortran 4.4.7 and 5.0.0.

Copyright Danail Obreschkow (danail.obreschkow@icrar.org), 2017-2018


SIMPLE USE
==========================================================================================================

Compile using
> make clean; make

Run using
> ./readbyte inputfilename index [number] [step]

where
index = index, of first byte to read (index = 1 is the first byte in the file)
number = number of single bytes and strings of 4/8 bytes to read from the file
step = step bytes between successive objects